To form a more perfect empire, Christopher, Emperor of Tamriel, 
has called for a governing document to ensure the safety of all peoples depending on our beautiful and holy empire, 
to ensure the preservation of democracy and unity within our beautiful and holy empire, 
and to ensure the legitimacy of the word of our most eminent and holy Tamrielic emperor. 


Signed, 
Christopher

By the Nine Divines of Tamriel, His Most Eminent Majesty, The Most High and Holy Christopher, First of His Name, 
Ysmir of Akatosh, Emperor of Cyrodiil, Dragon of the North, and Sovereign of His other Realms and Territories
